free.chessclub
Class MoveStruct

java.lang.Object
  free.chessclub.MoveStruct

public class MoveStruct
extends java.lang.Object

A container for information the chessclub.com server sends for a single move. Note that the fields only contain valid information if the setting turning on the sending of that information is on. For example, if DG_MOVE_SMITH is off, a MoveStruct arriving within a DG_SEND_MOVES datagram will contain an invalid (garbage) smithMove field. See ftp://ftp.chessclub.com/pub/icc/formats/formats.txt for information which settings turn on sending which fields.
